>\n<br />\n即刻投訴靜哂<br />\n<br />\n2邊都咁on9 打和啦"},{"pid":"67e3db24a037c3991b0bb7d054f9d6392610451a","tid":716308,"uid":52459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T07:33:23.000Z","msg":"有無攪錯呀，掛晒女人底褲出來屋企無男人架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac055c26e16e1192ac226f0b7dd57858119fa3aa","tid":716308,"uid":145923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T07:35:38.000Z","msg":"講粗口都性騷擾啦,胸圍底褲出埋實物.無理由唔係丫."},{"pid":"a6582c554d460467a9d998a2780e2f7b10145dbf","tid":716308,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T07:38:49.000Z","msg":"諗起四年前舊登個post<br />\n[沙田第一城] 網上真係好多痴線女人- 香港高登討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=EP&amp;message=5190417&amp;highlight_id=0&amp;page=1&amp;authorOnly=False\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DEP%26message%3D5190417%26highlight_id%3D0%26page%3D1%26authorOnly%3DFalse&d=2cyo8dFeyNMIOGkW81WWsvM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=f4d59abd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=EP&amp;message=5190417&amp;highlight_id=0&amp;page=1&amp;authorOnly=False</a><br />\n<br />\n啲片del 哂 得返呢條<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dailymotion.com/video/x4hdspj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymotion.com%2Fvideo%2Fx4hdspj&d=2cyo8dFeyNMIOGkW81WWsvM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=29794d11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymotion.com/video/x4hdspj</a>"},{"pid":"15383a09e22b7cc2d0c1168ccebe7766088ba29a","tid":716308,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T07:39:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8e5343c30c2503f67f659c72760696500717feb6","tid":716308,"uid":67500,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T08:49:23.000Z","msg":"大力關門製造噪音、在走廊燒衣紙<br />\n<br />\n屌柒佢老母啦"},{"pid":"50c